deserves him.

64
00:03:14,420 --> 00:03:15,360
I'm not like that.

65
00:03:17,420 --> 00:03:18,360
Alright, alright.

66
00:03:18,500 --> 00:03:19,660
You're just a little girl,

67
00:03:19,660 --> 00:03:20,600
