one step closer to my dream.

633
00:29:24,820 --> 00:29:25,740
Me?

634
00:29:26,940 --> 00:29:28,780
When I first started the business,

635
00:29:29,860 --> 00:29:30,940
I always imagined a day when

636
00:29:30,940 --> 00:29:32,900
I could work side by side

637
00:29:33,620 --> 00:29:34,580
with the one I love.

638
00:29:35,000 --> 00:29:36,420
We'd pull late nights
and grab midnight snacks,

639
00:29:37,200 --> 00:29:38,780
then take a walk home together.

640
00:29:39,300 --> 00:29:40,180
But you know,

641
00:29:40,180 --> 00:29:42,180
the only person by my side
has been Li Ao.

642
00:29:42,180 --> 00:29:43,380
So I'm not into working late.

643
00:29:44,940 --> 00:29:47,860
Well, congratulations.
You got exactly what you wished for.

644
00:29:48,870 --> 00:29:50,420
To show my thanks,

645
00:29:50,420 --> 00:29:52,020
I specially drew you a sketch.

646
00:29:52,500 --> 00:29:54,220
Please have a look, dear.

647
00:29:59,860 --> 00:30:01,140
This is me?

648
00:30:01,140 --> 00:30:02,060
Yeah.

649
00:30:02,940 --> 00:30:04,380
Thank you again.

650
00:30:04,780 --> 00:30:06,500
You have to keep this safe.

651
00:30:06,500 --> 00:30:07,500
Maybe I'll become famous

652
00:30:07,500 --> 00:30:09,780
and this artwork will be quite valuable.

653
00:30:10,100 --> 00:30:11,180
I'll get it framed for you.

654
00:30:11,380 --> 00:30:12,300
Yeah.

655
00:30:12,620 --> 00:30:13,540
Keep it safe.

656
00:30:16,220 --> 00:30:17,140
Here.

657
00:30:26,620 --> 00:30:29,340
Drink less. You're treating wine
like magic potion.

658
00:30:29,350 --> 00:30:30,700
I wish that were true.

659
00:30:31,580 --> 00:30:33,380
You and Xinran have fought before.

660
00:30:33,380 --> 00:30:35,260
- Is it really that serious?
- This time it's different!

661
00:30:35,820 --> 00:30:37,500
Keep your voice down.
What are you doing?

662
00:30:39,980 --> 00:30:41,300
I'll tell you a secret.

663
00:30:43,310 --> 00:30:45,180
I became a relationship expert

664
00:30:45,180 --> 00:30:46,700
because I'm actually afraid of love.

665
00:30:47,940 --> 00:30:50,900
What remarkable woman hurt you so badly?

666
00:30:51,540 --> 00:30:52,420
Enough.

667
00:30:52,420 --> 00:30:55,300
Not a remarkable woman.
It was my parents.

668
00:30:57,580 --> 00:30:58,500
Your parents?

669
00:31:00,980 --> 00:31:01,900
When I was a kid,

670
00:31:02,460 --> 00:31:04,100
they argued about getting divorced

671
00:31:04,860 --> 00:31:06,300
and always made me choose a side.

672
00:31:08,300 --> 00:31:10,780
I just wanted to understand
what love really is

673
00:31:11,220 --> 00:31:12,740
to change two people like that.

674
00:31:13,660 --> 00:31:14,580
So,

675
00:31:15,020 --> 00:31:18,060
I decided to study love psychology,

676
00:31:19,340 --> 00:31:21,780
hoping they could
mend a broken relationship.

677
00:31:24,300 --> 00:31:25,420
Guess what happened?

678
00:31:26,960 --> 00:31:28,580
They still ended up apart.

679
00:31:28,580 --> 00:31:29,780
And then no one wanted me.

680
00:31:34,020 --> 00:31:36,260
I thought me and Xinran
would be different,

681
00:31:36,940 --> 00:31:37,860
but,

682
00:31:38,300 --> 00:31:39,900
I was still an empty glass.

683
00:31:43,020 --> 00:31:44,780
I couldn't even manage my own love life.

684
00:31:44,780 --> 00:31:46,540
How could I call myself
a relationship expert?

685
00:31:46,540 --> 00:31:47,580
It's really ironic.

686
00:31:48,740 --> 00:31:52,380
Actually, if you said this to Xinran,

687
00:31:52,380 --> 00:31:53,420
she would understand you.

688
00:31:58,020 --> 00:31:59,140
But I'm a man,

689
00:32:01,220 --> 00:32:02,740
how could I possibly

690
00:32:02,740 --> 00:32:05,700
tell the woman I like

691
00:32:08,300 --> 00:32:09,740
that I'm actually very lonely?

692
00:32:11,340 --> 00:32:12,260
Wen Cheng.

693
00:32:12,780 --> 00:32:15,340
If you don't say this,
she'll never know.

694
00:32:16,780 --> 00:32:18,580
If you miss out because of this,

695
00:32:19,260 --> 00:32:20,580
wouldn't that be such a shame?

696
00:32:22,580 --> 00:32:24,050
If everyone in the world

697
00:32:24,460 --> 00:32:26,660
could just speak their true feelings,

698
00:32:27,940 --> 00:32:29,620
wouldn't the world be at peace?

699
00:32:29,620 --> 00:32:30,620
No misunderstandings,

700
00:32:31,220 --> 00:32:32,740
no tangled feelings to deal with.

701
00:32:35,300 --> 00:32:36,220
That's true.

702
00:32:36,980 --> 00:32:38,500
Some things are just too hard to say

703
00:32:39,940 --> 00:32:42,300
because there's a barrier
inside your heart you can't cross.

704
00:32:43,140 --> 00:32:44,060
Wen Cheng.

705
00:32:49,060 --> 00:32:49,980
You're right.

706
00:33:03,500 --> 00:33:04,780
I think Jianing's approach

707
00:33:04,780 --> 00:33:05,980
isn't entirely wrong.

708
00:33:06,620 --> 00:33:07,660
But how exactly

709
00:33:07,660 --> 00:33:10,100
can we get young women
to fit into the tea plantation?

710
00:33:10,100 --> 00:33:11,340
Now that's the real question.

711
00:33:15,500 --> 00:33:17,100
Still having a meeting this late?

712
00:33:17,460 --> 00:33:18,700
You're lousy at your job.

713
00:33:19,300 --> 00:33:20,980
Why are you still at Yao Yuan's place?

714
00:33:21,740 --> 00:33:23,380
Do I need a reason
to be with my girlfriend?

715
00:33:26,140 --> 00:33:27,660
