716
00:33:27,660 --> 00:33:28,620
Don't come and distract me.

717
00:33:29,860 --> 00:33:31,550
I'm here to help.

718
00:33:31,780 --> 00:33:32,700
No, thanks.

719
00:33:34,140 --> 00:33:35,820
I'll report to you tomorrow.

720
00:33:35,820 --> 00:33:37,100
If you help me today,

721
00:33:37,100 --> 00:33:38,060
