that suits your taste.

739
00:34:29,020 --> 00:34:30,100
Like a young girl,

740
00:34:30,100 --> 00:34:31,340
in the vast crowd,

741
00:34:31,340 --> 00:34:33,380
you're sure to find your bestie.

742
00:34:34,020 --> 00:34:36,620
So for this campaign's image and ad,

743
00:34:36,620 --> 00:34:37,580
we want to

744
00:34:37,580 --> 00:34:39,500
(Xiduomeng Tea Proposal Report)
feature young women on screen.

745
00:34:40,140 --> 00:34:42,300
Tea feels traditional and serious,

746
00:34:42,300 --> 00:34:43,820
so we need something young

747
00:34:43,820 --> 00:34:44,940
and lively

748
00:34:44,940 --> 00:34:45,860
to break that image.

749
00:34:46,780 --> 00:34:49,180
And this campaign's core theme

750
00:34:49,180 --> 00:34:50,500
will focus on besties.

751
00:34:50,980 --> 00:34:53,380
We want Xiduomeng Tea
to become the brand

752
00:34:53,380 --> 00:34:56,180
that understands consumers best.

753
00:34:58,980 --> 00:34:59,860
Mr. Jiang,

754
00:34:59,860 --> 00:35:01,860
this proposal was
put together too quickly.

755
00:35:01,860 --> 00:35:03,260
I've already asked them to redo...

756
00:35:10,380 --> 00:35:12,020
In such a short time,

757
00:35:12,020 --> 00:35:14,900
you came up with such a concise
and powerful proposal,

758
00:35:14,900 --> 00:35:17,260
while keeping tradition
yet adding fresh ideas.

759
00:35:17,540 --> 00:35:18,820
It's really impressive.

760
00:35:18,820 --> 00:35:19,740
This is fantastic!

761
00:35:21,220 --> 00:35:23,500
You'd break your hands clapping.

762
00:35:25,260 --> 00:35:27,060
Weren't we supposed to stay impartial?

763
00:35:28,260 --> 00:35:29,660
She did such a good job.

764
00:35:29,660 --> 00:35:31,020
I have no reason not to praise her.

765
00:35:31,300 --> 00:35:32,500
Of course you can.

766
00:35:32,500 --> 00:35:33,340
Then please

767
00:35:33,340 --> 00:35:34,980
treat the other colleagues the same way.

768
00:35:35,420 --> 00:35:37,060
Don't just we're all
supposed to do well.

769
00:35:37,860 --> 00:35:38,780
Hmm.

770
00:35:39,420 --> 00:35:40,340
Meeting adjourned.

771
00:35:54,100 --> 00:35:55,540
Are you still upset?

772
00:35:55,540 --> 00:35:56,460
I'm not.

773
00:35:59,260 --> 00:36:00,180
That's good.

774
00:36:00,660 --> 00:36:02,340
Didn't you say you really wanted to try

775
00:36:02,340 --> 00:36:03,860
