805
00:37:42,740 --> 00:37:44,060
Anlan's girlfriend?

806
00:37:45,380 --> 00:37:47,060
This is my first time meeting her.

807
00:37:47,740 --> 00:37:48,620
Yao.

808
00:37:48,620 --> 00:37:50,700
This is Anlan's aunt, and Ms. Lin.

809
00:37:51,780 --> 00:37:52,700
Nice to meet you both.

810
00:37:52,900 --> 00:37:53,820
I'm Yao Yuan.

811
00:37:55,820 --> 00:37:57,660
Since we ran into each other,
let's sit together.

812
00:37:57,660 --> 00:37:58,580
Sure.

813
00:37:59,100 --> 00:38:00,500
Someone's treating us now.

814
00:38:05,980 --> 00:38:07,340
Eat more, don't hold back.

815
00:38:09,780 --> 00:38:10,820
Miss Yao,

816
00:38:10,820 --> 00:38:12,100
how old are you this year?

817
00:38:12,100 --> 00:38:13,500
What did you major in?

818
00:38:13,500 --> 00:38:14,420
Where do you work?

819
00:38:16,980 --> 00:38:18,100
Just call me Yuan.

820
00:38:18,460 --> 00:38:19,500
I'm 25 years old.

821
00:38:19,900 --> 00:38:21,980
Now I work at
an art organization in Jiangning

822
00:38:21,980 --> 00:38:22,940
as an exhibition planner.

823
00:38:23,460 --> 00:38:24,780
It's summer break now.

824
00:38:24,780 --> 00:38:26,460
I'm helping in Anlan's company
with curation.

825
00:38:26,700 --> 00:38:28,420
Then you must be really talented.

826
00:38:29,380 --> 00:38:31,460
I also work at Anlan's company.

827
00:38:31,860 --> 00:38:33,140
Yao is one of the elite talents

828
00:38:33,140 --> 00:38:34,940
specially hired by Anlan.

829
00:38:35,710 --> 00:38:36,690
Mrs. Jiang,

830
00:38:36,980 --> 00:38:38,180
you're asking so many questions.

831
00:38:38,180 --> 00:38:39,980
Are you doing a background check?

832
00:38:40,540 --> 00:38:42,060
What background check?

833
00:38:42,260 --> 00:38:43,940
Maybe one day we'll be family.

834
00:38:44,260 --> 00:38:45,780
Of course I want to know more.

835
00:38:46,220 --> 00:38:47,500
Is it right, Yuan?

836
00:38:50,020 --> 00:38:51,060
I'm going to the restroom.

837
00:38:51,540 --> 00:38:52,390
Okay.

838
00:38:52,390 --> 00:38:53,230
I'll go with you.

839
00:39:03,140 --> 00:39:04,100
How come Anlan's dating

840
00:39:04,100 --> 00:39:05,820
such a shabby girl?

841
00:39:05,820 --> 00:39:07,060
Tell me about it.

842
00:39:07,060 --> 00:39:09,420
Anlan is the golden bachelor
of the social circle.

843
00:39:09,820 --> 00:39:11,460
He turns down all kinds of girls.

844
00:39:11,780 --> 00:39:14,780
Yet he chose someone so unremarkable.

